description: [PR Newswire] - BRAMPTON, ON, Jan. 11, 2017 /CNW/ - Loblaw Companies Limited (TSX:L.TO) announced today that it will release its fourth quarter 2016 results on February 23, 2017 at 6:30 a.m. (ET). To access Loblaw's fourth quarter conference call, please dial (416) 642-5209 or (866) 222-0265. Loblaw Companies Limited is Canada's food and pharmacy leader, the nation's largest retailer, and the majority unitholder of Choice Properties Real Estate Investment Trust.
